{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:SS11SwiftExtrasE8sdbmhashSivp","modules":[{"relatedModules":["Swift"],"name":"SwiftExtras"}],"symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","extendedModule":"Swift","title":"sdbmhash","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sdbmhash"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This algorithm was created for sdbm (a public-domain reimplementation of ndbm) database library.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it was found to do well in scrambling bits, causing better distribution of the keys and fewer splits.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it also happens to be a good general hashing function with good distribution.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual function is hash(i) = hash(i - 1) * 65599 + str[i];","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"what is included below is the faster version used in gawk.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[there is even a faster, duff-device version] the magic prime constant 65599 (2^6 + 2^16 - 1)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"was picked out of thin air while experimenting with many different constants.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this is one of the algorithms used in berkeley db (see sleepycat) and elsewhere.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Hashed string","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String"]]},"references":{"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift","title":"Swift"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string","type":"topic","title":"String","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"text":"extension","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"String","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras/Swift/String/sdbmhash":{"title":"sdbmhash","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hashed string"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sdbmhash","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftExtras\/documentation\/SwiftExtras\/Swift\/String\/sdbmhash","url":"\/documentation\/swiftextras\/swift\/string\/sdbmhash","type":"topic"},"doc://SwiftExtras/documentation/SwiftExtras":{"title":"SwiftExtras","role":"collection","abstract":[],"type":"